public int getNextWalkingDirection() { if(wQueueReadPtr == wQueueWritePtr) return -1; // walking queue empty int dir; do { dir = misc.direction(currentX, currentY, walkingQueueX[wQueueReadPtr], walkingQueueY[wQueueReadPtr]); if(dir == -1) wQueueReadPtr = (wQueueReadPtr+1) % walkingQueueSize; else if((dir&1) != 0) { println_debug("Invalid waypoint in walking queue!"); disconnected = true; resetWalkingQueue(); return -1; } } while(dir == -1 && wQueueReadPtr != wQueueWritePtr); if(dir == -1) return -1; dir >>= 1; currentX += misc.directionDeltaX[dir]; currentY += misc.directionDeltaY[dir]; absX += misc.directionDeltaX[dir]; absY += misc.directionDeltaY[dir]; return dir; }
